/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"这听起来也许是显而易见的道理，但我认为多数人对健康的投入都远远不够，往往等到真的生病了才开始重视。"},"155":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-73","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"锻炼、睡眠和饮食能带来巨大变化（比如快乐 +30%，精力 +50%，成果也 +50%），但却总被我们忽略。"},"156":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-74","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"顺便说一句，非常推荐 Huberman 的播客，值得一听。🙂"},"157":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-75","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"做课余项目通常很有价值，它们可以："},"158":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-76","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"向雇主展示你的经验、兴趣和价值观"},"159":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-77","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"帮你探索新主题、新想法"},"160":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-78","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"积累实践经验、洞察力和直觉"},"161":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-79","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"创造出真正有用的东西"},"162":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-80","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"或者纯粹是为了好玩！"},"163":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-81","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":